<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>26</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zǒu jìn xīn de yī tiān, xīn zhōng tián měi huān xǐ,
 kǒu zhōng fā chū dì yī jù huà, zhǔ a wǒ gǎn xiè nǐ!
 cì xià nǐ de ēn qīng, mù yù zài nǐ de ài lǐ,
 hū huàn zhe wǒ de míng zì, bǎ wǒ dài jìn nǐ de suì yuè lǐ.
 hū huàn zhe wǒ de míng zì, bǎ wǒ dài jìn nǐ de suì yuè lǐ.
 jué xīn yào bǎ fú yīn chuán biàn cūn luò shān gǔ hé xiǎo xī,
 yī bù yī bù de zǒu xià qù, yī bù yī bù zǒu dào dǐ,
 xīn de yī tiān, xīn de shí dài lǐ, zhǔ a wǒ chuán yáng nǐ!</lyrics>
<title>zǒu jìn xīn de yī tiān 迦南26</title>
</song>